room_title: Escape room "We're All Mad Here" by Escaped In Time in Colorado Springs
room_description:
Curiosity has gotten the best of you again. You see a strange opening in the wall and decide to investigate. You are sucked into the hole and suddenly you find yourself transported to a strange land full of adventure and wonder.
At first it is exciting, but you quickly realize that you don't know how to get home. If you cannot unravel the mysterious rules of the land, you may be trapped here forever!
